QuantumGameOfLifeHamiltonian\\\", \\\"[\\\", StyleBox[\\\"L\\\", \\\"TI\\\"], \
\\\",\\\", StyleBox[\\\"opts\\\", \\\"TI\\\"], \\\"]\\\"}], \\\"MR\\\"]\\) \
returns the Hamiltonian for the Quantum Game of Life (QGL)   model for a \
spin-1/2 chain of length \\!\\(\\*StyleBox[\\\"L\\\", \\\"TI\\\"]\\) \
(arXiv:2510.16570):\\n\\!\\(\\)  H = \[Sum] \
\\!\\(\\*SuperscriptBox[SubscriptBox[\\\"\[Sigma]\\\", \\\"i\\\"], \\\"x\\\"]\
\\) (\\!\\(\\*SuperscriptBox[SubscriptBox[\\\"\[ScriptN]\\\", \\\"i\\\"], \
\\\"2\\\"]\\) + \\!\\(\\*SuperscriptBox[SubscriptBox[\\\"\[ScriptN]\\\", \
\\\"i\\\"], \\\"3\\\"]\\)).\\n\\!\\(\\)  \\n\\!\\(\\)  Options:\\n\\!\\(\\)  \
Momentum -> \\\"All\\\" (default) | Integer k (0 <= k < L).\\n\\!\\(\\)  \
Parity -> \\\"None\\\" (default) | 1 | -1.\\n\\!\\(\\)  \\n\\!\\(\\)  Note: \
Parity projection (Inversion Symmetry) is only valid for Momentum sectors k=0 \
or k=L/2.\"\>", "InformationUsageText",
